# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Use depth first search approach,
1. Go to left, if it matches one of the values then return the node else return null.
2. Then go right and do the same.
3. If both returns null then that particular node is our LCA.

# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(N)
